('e350a80f-683e-5dd3-a59d-595a1ea531e9', 1, 'owner_age_proxy_rpls_tenure', 'positive', NULL, 'Senior RPLS Larry James Pollok (TBPELS license #5186) granted 1996-06-07 → 30yr tenure. TX RPLS requires 4yr college + 4yr supervised survey-in-training + state exam (typically earned at age 28-35); est. owner age ~60.', 'tbpels_rpls_roster', 'https://tbpedownloads.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rpls_roster.csv', '2026-05-16'),
